  <div id="wz"><span class="wzword">您的位置：首页 >> 通知公告</span></div>
	<div id="main">	
	
	   <div id="all_content"> 

	     <div class="MainNewsTitle">
	     <h1>西藏民族大学附属医院充电桩合作运营公告</h1>
	     </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsUpdate">
				      发布时间：2022-11-24
				      
				      信息来源：附属医院　　浏览次数：38440 </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsAction" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;">
				      <script type="text/javascript">writeColor("common/scripts/color/");</script>
				      【<a href="javascript:doZoom('16px');">大</a> <a href="javascript:doZoom('14px');">中</a> <a href="javascript:doZoom('12px');">小</a>】【<a href="javascript:printWindow();">打印本页</a>】【<a href="javascript:closeWindow();">关闭窗口</a>】</div>
				    <div class="MainNewsAction">
				      
         </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsContent" id="content" style="table-layout:fixed;">&nbsp;<b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">一、基本情况</span></b>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">西藏民族大学附属医院综合楼现已经启用，为</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">给医院职工、患者提供一个良好的保障服务，经医院研究决定</font><font face="宋体">采用合作方式建设我院充电桩项目。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">二、项目概况及合作内容</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、项目概况：西藏民族大学附属医院充电桩项目位于咸阳市渭城区文汇东路6号西藏民族大学附属医院综合楼负一层，共9个停车位。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、合作内容：医院负责提供场地和电源，合作企业负责提供、安装充电桩及日常维护运营。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">、充电桩安装要求：</font><font face="宋体">9个充电车位，以3</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">0</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">千瓦以上充电桩为主，在磋商谈判时确定，签订协议后在</font><font face="宋体">1月内充电桩安装完毕，尽快为我院员工及患者提供正常服务。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">、充电收费和利润分成：我院用电费用约</font><font face="宋体">0</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">.58</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">元</font><font face="宋体">/度，充电费按市场价格收取，磋商谈判时确定利润分配方案。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">5、合作期限：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">5</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">年</font> </span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">三、合作方资格要求</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1、具备有效的企业营业执照。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、法定代表人直接参加磋商，须出具法定代表人身份证，非法定代表人参加磋商，须出具法定代表人授权书及被授权人身份证；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;">四、竞争性磋商响应文件递交方式：</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">1、</font><font face="宋体">磋商响应</font><font face="宋体">文件递交截止时间：已报名的供应商请于</font><font face="宋体">2022年1</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">月</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">1</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">日前将磋商响应文件送至西藏民族附属医院门诊楼</font><font face="宋体">3楼后勤办公室（民院十字）；如因疫情等因素变化使项目变动的，另行通知。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2、联系电话：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">13891474455</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">联系人：梁贵年</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">3、磋商时间： 2022 年</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">12</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;<font face="宋体">月</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">2</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">日上午</font><font face="宋体">10:00</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">4、磋商地点：西藏民族大学附属医院综合楼十七楼017室。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font face="宋体">西藏民族大学附属医院</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:15.0000pt;&#10;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
